value.name: Carson City sheriff's detectives ask for public's help identifying catalytic converter thief
value.description: Carson City Sheriff's Office investigators are asking for the public's help identifying a suspect involved in the theft of a catalytic converter that happened at a South Carson Street casino earlier this month.
